channel.title: How to add a Crystal Key Chest [ PI ]
channel.description: I'm just wondering if I can add a chest at my home in edgeville that uses a crystal key to unlock, most other servers have a chest and when you click on it it says "you need a crystal key and at least one inventory slot" and when u get the crystal key it gives you a good item, If you can help then please tell me how to add it! I think i would be able to add it by myself if i had the object id code for it.... so if you cant help, but know the code, please post that! Thanks, Adam.
